be.docarch.odt2braille.addon
Class Interpoint55PrintDialog

java.lang.Object
  be.docarch.odt2braille.addon.Interpoint55PrintDialog

public class Interpoint55PrintDialog
extends java.lang.Object

Show an OpenOffice.org dialog window for embossing with the Interpoint55 printer. With this dialog, a user can choose

  • the location for saving the .brf file,
  • the location of the wprint55 program folder,
  • a wprint55 configuration file (.ini), and
  • whether or not this configuration file should be overwritten by the new settings.
The user can only press OK if a save location is set, wprint55 is found and a configuration file is selected. Initial settings are loaded from the OpenOffice.org extension file (.oxt) and saved afterwards. The .ini file is overwritten if this option is checked. This class also has public methods for getting the .brf file location and executing the wprint55 program.

Author:
Bert Frees
